      geneious.plugin.FIMSUploadOperation

public class FIMSUploadOperation
extends com.biomatters.geneious.publicapi.plugin.DocumentOperation

Control the operation of the BiocodeFIMS upload operation, handling feedback from the system such as Warning Messages and redirecting output to appropriate places in the Geneious environment.

Author:
Matthew Cheung
